reviewText: I bought this box set because I have all of the previous box sets of Bleach. This box set was truly awesome, the battle with Aizen got very intense, that was most of the story in this box set. There is at least one weird episode, so be on the lookout. I definitely recommend this box set as long as you have the 20 box sets that came before this one.
